node.text: Congrats to Nick Angotti from Colorado — winner of last night’s #VirtualHerf royal humidor! Special thanks to humidor expert Mike Howe for joining us last night as well as our #GurkhaNation for a record attendance. See you all (virtually) again on Wednesday, October 14.

node.text: TOMORROW, Wednesday, September 9 at 8 PM (EDT) - Join our monthly virtual herf for your chance to WIN this royal humidor valued at $7,500! Special guest Mike Howe, humidor expert, will be joining us and talking all things humidors. Click the link in our bio to tune in.

node.text:
TOMORROW — You don't have to smoke and drink alone! 
Join Juan Lopez and special guest, @bacardi Brand Specialist @chatchowtv, for our weekly #VirtualHerf at 8 PM (EDT)! We’ll be smoking Gurkhas, making three cocktail pairings, giving out prizes, and answering your questions. To follow along with the @therealhavanaclub cocktail recipes, you’ll need:

Cuban Bishop
1½ oz. Havana Club Blanco
½ oz. lime juice
½ oz. simple syrup
½ oz. Sonoma Cabernet Sauvignon

Hemingway Daiquiri
1½ oz. Havana Club Blanco
½ oz. maraschino
3/4 oz. lime juice
½ oz. grapefruit juice
½ oz. cane syrup

Daiquiri
2 oz. Havana Club Blanco
1 oz. lime juice
3/4 oz. cane syrup

Join via Zoom by clicking the link in our bio. #GurkhaNation

node.text:
The Gurkha Heritage is a medium-bodied cigar full of robust flavors, hand-rolled in Nicaragua, and comes in a rare 35-count box. This cigar was blended by our blending team at American Caribbean Cigars in Nicaragua with the input of our in-house blender and VP of Sales Juan Lopez. 

Available in natural and maduro. #GurkhaNation
